   314→/**
   315→ * Determine actions based on confidence thresholds and category rules
   316→ */
   317→function determineActions(
   318→  assignedLabels: AssignedLabels,
   319→  aiClassificationResult: FinalClassification,
   320→  config: FinalDecisionConfig,
